divs: Sighting DetailsI was standing at my flat balcony on the top flour in a very high bulding at Amman CENTER,I WAS LOKING OVER THE CITY AND SUDENLY A BIG BALL OF LIGHT LIKE STAR APPEAR FLYING JUST OVER THE CITY in a low level,for about 3minets and then disappear.i WAS SURPRISED didn't know what was it and i thought I MAY FIND OUT THE NEXT DAY FROM THE PRESS BUT IT WASN'T MENTIONED!
